{
  "message": "fuzz(fj-conformance): add 12 smoke_harness_json corpus seeds\n\nStructured test inputs for JSON parser edge cases:\n- empty_object: Empty JSON object {}\n- fixture_note_long_suite: 200-char suite name\n- fixture_note_nested_brackets: Braces/brackets in strings\n- fixture_note_newlines: Newlines and tabs in notes\n- fixture_note_unicode_escapes: Unicode escape sequences\n- parity_cases_numeric_strings: Numeric values as strings\n- parity_cases_single_mismatch: Single element mismatch\n- parity_cases_special_chars: Quotes, backslashes, slashes\n- parity_cases_whitespace: Whitespace variations in JSON\n- parity_report_all_zeros: All-zero counts\n- parity_report_large_numbers: Large numeric values\n- parity_report_u64_max: u64::MAX values (overflow test)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
